abstract_ssm: Collection of engravings by the French engraver Charles Balthazar Julien Fevret de Saint-Saint-Mémin. Most are profile portrait engravings, but several early views of New York City are also included.
title_ssm: Saint-Mémin and the Neoclassical Profile Portrait in the America
The St-Memin Collection of Portraits, with photographs of 760 etchings by Gurney & Son
